name: massachusetts-bay-internal-wave-packets-digitized-from-sar-imagery-and-intersected-with-a-bathdf6ff
notes: This feature class contains internal wave packets digitized from SAR imagery and intersected with a bathymetrically derived slope surface for Massachusetts Bay. The internal wave packets were digitized at a 1:350,000 scale and the degree slope surface had a 360 x 360 meter resolution.
